{"tid":2437530,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"這怎麼做到？少時Tiffany喝出5杯開水味道差別　全場嚇傻","createTime":"2021-03-08T02:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T23:08:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":95,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ef0e105cabf602a8fe92a21dfe031b0476bf3e","tid":2437530,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:32:37.000Z","msg":"南韓女團少女時代成員蒂芬妮（Tiffany）有著甜美嗓音，為了保養喉嚨，不論是在彩排、演唱會、日常生活中，她都會盡量多喝水，喝著喝著卻意外練就喝水猜品牌的技能，她6日出演綜藝節目《認識的哥哥》展現特殊長才，還能說出每個品牌礦泉水的味道差異，令看得主持人目瞪口呆，連李壽根都感到不可思議提問「這要怎麼猜對」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5489/d5489408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5489%2Fd5489408.jpg&h=0f108a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Tiffany喝水，竟可以準確猜出礦泉水的品牌。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5489/d5489412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5489%2Fd5489412.jpg&h=89ab82fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒂芬妮6日出演綜藝節目《認識的哥哥》，自信滿滿表示能夠猜對不同礦泉水品牌的味道，節目組遞上5杯外觀一模一樣的透明水杯，她依舊可以區分每杯水的品牌，分別說出水質差異，例如2號杯的口感滑順，且還帶點香味，3號杯則是尾韻較清淡，喝開水彷彿是品嚐紅酒一般，且她正確猜出5杯品牌，過人的技能連主持人都感到詫異。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5489/d5489411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5489%2Fd5489411.jpg&h=0724851f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼少時Tiffany講出水的差異被封為「絕對味覺」。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5489/d5489409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5489%2Fd5489409.jpg&h=c3ba8ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了秀出超猛技能，蒂芬妮當天也帶給粉絲一則重大訊息，由於她的生日是8月1日，少女時代的出道日則是8月5日，她鬆口表示少女時代有很大機會在8月以完全體一起上《認識的哥哥》，這則消息釋出後，令粉絲對少女時代睽違4年的合體相當期待。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tv.naver.com/v/18832738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.naver.com%2Fv%2F18832738&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=827c1070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tv.naver.com/v/18832738</a>"},{"pid":"484cd7556ee9c6c2d32408e37550bc9f7732cbed","tid":2437530,"uid":93096,"like":142,"dislike":3,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"pr咁早開工..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f39d176b0df905ece0b421304ea2849fc8ea42","tid":2437530,"uid":28558,"like":355,"dislike":16,"score":339,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"含撚時有冇絕對味覺<br />\n一含就知邊個男人"},{"pid":"01ba2486000d0bd3681eb4611340cf51660b588b","tid":2437530,"uid":224533,"like":180,"dislike":8,"score":172,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"有哂劇本有幾難，加上你又驗證唔到<br />\n<br />\n馬總統看手錶"},{"pid":"4a034d90ee7b907ffe7f5013087b2162db8f44ba","tid":2437530,"uid":6192,"like":449,"dislike":2,"score":447,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"根本唔同牌子水<br />\n味道真係有分別<br />\n分到有咩出奇"},{"pid":"c3212da70fc4592b31787223418db140654fe803","tid":2437530,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484cd7556ee9c6c2d32408e37550bc9f7732cbed","tid":2437530,"uid":93096,"like":142,"dislike":3,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"pr咁早開工..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"我無收錢的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07641f6d80825fbe5b168a91d8ccdc038eb22e7","tid":2437530,"uid":261849,"like":43,"dislike":6,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"e3f39d176b0df905ece0b421304ea2849fc8ea42","tid":2437530,"uid":28558,"like":355,"dislike":16,"score":339,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"含撚時有冇絕對味覺<br />\n一含就知邊個男人"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:49:21.000Z","msg":"應該係含撚個陣練出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827531eac0a5bc96260d1a98999a99a67a1d46b4","tid":2437530,"uid":28558,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"q